  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_3",
    "text": "1.在下面的实物图上圈出本课所学的字，并和拼音连线。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08251900108577633,
