  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_5",
    "text": "2.重点字词练习。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0781758957654723,
      0.39351851851851855,
      0.32138979370249726,
      0.41512345679012347
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_6",
    "text": "（1）为句中加点的多音字选择恰当的读音。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10206297502714441,
      0.41975308641975306,
      0.5342019543973942,
      0.4398148148148148
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_7",
    "text": "A.kōng B.kòng",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.40390879478827363,
      0.4537037037037037,
      0.5841476655808904,
      0.47530864197530864
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_8",
    "text": "①外面的空（ ）地上放了很多空（ ）瓶子。 ②早晨的空（ ）气很清新，空（ ）闲时，我都会早起锻炼。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15200868621064062,
      0.48148148148148145,
      0.8360477741585234,
      0.5324074074074074
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_9",
    "text": "（2）用“√”画出加点字的正确读音。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10423452768729642,
      0.5385802469135802,
      0.49077090119435396,
      0.5601851851851852
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_10",
    "text": "①天阴沉沉（chénchen）的，快要下雨啦！ ②小草从土里探出头来，伸（sēn shēn）了伸懒腰。 ③他被雨淋得全身湿（shisī）淋淋的。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15200868621064062,
      0.5694444444444444,
      0.6536373507057546,
      0.6419753086419753
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_11",
    "text": "（3）按要求填空。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10423452768729642,
      0.6496913580246914,
      0.28447339847991315,
      0.6697530864197531
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_12",
    "text": "①“潮”字的部首是 ，带这个部首的宇大多和水有关，我还知道其他 带这个部首的字： % ~ 0 ②有在有，可组为 0",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14115092290988057,
      0.6790123456790124,
      0.9207383279044516,
      0.7839506172839507
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_13",
    "text": "二、会用",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.08034744842562432,
      0.7901234567901234,
      0.18675352877307275,
      0.8117283950617284
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_14",
    "text": "3.选择正确的感叹词或疑问词填空。（每个字只用一次）",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08251900108577633,
      0.8287037037037037,
      0.8425624321389794,
      0.8503086419753086
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1408_15",
    "text": "（1）小白兔大声喊：“燕子，燕子，你为什么飞得这么低 2 （2）小鱼说：“小白兔，你快回家 ，小心淋着雨。 1 （3）一只大蚂蚊说：“是要下雨了，我们正忙着搬东西 1\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
